  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/2412",
  "title": "ClearAll widget remove configuration preset",
  "body": "On IS if you combine a `ClearAll` component with a widget who takes a preset configuration, the later will be remove by the widget. \r\n\r\nFor example `RangeSlider` accept a `min` & `max` options to restrict the search on specific range. If we combine this widget with `ClearAll` the user will able to erase the preset range.\r\n\r\n**Example:**\r\n\r\n* the slider is set with a min value of `10` & max value of `500`\r\n* update the min value of the slider (ex: `90`)\r\n* click on clearAll\r\n* trigger a search from the `SearchBox` (ex: `mg`)\r\n\r\nThe bounds has been erased.\r\n\r\nhttps://jsfiddle.net/tksyn43f/2",
